0:\"LYT_LAYOUT\";s:7:\"default\";s:28:\"LYT_LAYOUT_APPLY_TO_CHILDREN\";s:1:\"1\";s:25:\"LYT_LAYOUT_SUBPAGECONTENT\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"LYT_STYLESHEET\";s:4:\"main\";s:15:\"LYT_WINDOWTITLE\";s:0:\"\";}',0,NULL,NULL,15,634,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(683,'Referral Program FAQs',NULL,'2004-12-15 08:59:58',1,'a:1:{s:20:\"AST_PAGE_PAGECONTENT\";s:8937:\"<p class=\"textHeader\">Introducing the Llama Export Referral Program </p><p>We have developed a Referral Program that you can join online from our website. Joining is optional, and you can continue to purchase llamas from Llama Export even if you choose not to participate in our referral programme. However, we highly recommend that you do join the programme, as you will receive points on sales generated through your sales network. Once you qualify with enough points you will receive a gift from Llama Export from our Frequent Buyer Programme.</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" width=\"50\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">What exactly is the Llama Export Referral Programme?</p><p>It is a Multi Level Referral system that has been designed to help you earn more points which help you qualify for a gift from our Frequent Buyer Program. You can join the Llama Export referral programme online through our website by choosing a login and password. You will then receive points on every purchase you make, and when you recommend Llama Export you will receive points every time a member of your sales network places an order through our website (up to the fourth level of your sales network).</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">How does it work?</p><p>Our referral programme is simple but very effective. It?s like a chain reaction. You tell two people about Llama Export who tell two people and before you know it you will have developed a sales network.</p><p>The ?Sales Network? has 4 levels. The 1st level consists of &quot;online buyers&quot; that you find who refer to your Login when they register. The 2nd level represents &quot;online buyers&quot; that the 1st level finds, who register referring to their Login. Then, 2nd level buyers will find other buyers, 3rd level, who in turn, will find others, 4th level. You will receive points on all the items that the &quot;online buyers&quot; in the 1st, 2nd, 3rd, and 4th levels of your network buy.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">How do I register?</p><p>Go to the <a href=\"http://www.llamaexport.com/Members\">members</a> page to register. Enter your username and password along with your referrer?s password. If there is no referrer, leave this field blank. Complete all of the required fields within the form and click on submit. </p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">Is there a fee to join the Llama Export referral programme? </p><p>No. Participation in our programme is free of charge.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p><span class=\"textHeader\">Do I receive points on my own orders? </span></p><p>Yes, you receive 1 point for every 1 Euro you spend.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">How many points do I receive on orders made by my sales network?</p><p>For every purchase within your sales network you will receive 10 points regardless of the value of the order.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">What is the exact amount that is distributed by Llama Export Referral? </p><p>The amount awarded by Llama Export referral is that of the points your own personal orders generate and the points awarded to you from the sales made through your sales network (up to four levels). </p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">How exactly does it work?</p><p>Once you are registered in the programme you will receive points on your purchases through AcmeRockets.com and if someone registers with your username, you will receive points on their orders. For example: you tell your friends about Llama Export and they register referring to your username and they start buying their llamas from Llama Export. You will now have your 1st level and will receive points on every item they buy through the Llama Export website. When they tell their friends (who register referring to their username), you will have a 2nd level, and you again receive points on their purchases; when a 2nd level tells someone else, and they buy, you receive points on your 3rd level; you receive points when your 3rd level participants tell someone else, right down to your 4th level. </p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">How is \'My Login\' used? </p><p>If you want to earn points through the Llama Export referral programme, give your username to others who want to buy at AcmeRockets.com. Because they have registered with your details they are added to your \'Sales Network\', and you will receive points for every order they place through the Llama Export website.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">Can I utilize my accumulated points for a third party? </p><p>No, you need to use them for your own gift.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"dotline\" valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\"></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"EMB: 589\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=589\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\"><p class=\"textHeader\">If a customer in my sales network returns their purchase, will the points be deducted? </p><p>Points are awarded after a sale is confirmed and the credit card is processed. Should the purchaser wish to return the goods or cancel their order after this point in time, Llama Export has the right to alter your total points allocated deducting any points awarded for these failed purchases. </p></td></tr></tbody></table><br /><br /><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"80%\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"boxleftfill\" valign=\"top\" align=\"left\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\"><img alt=\"EMB: 584\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=584\" border=\"0\" /></td><td class=\"boxtopfill\" height=\"7\"><img alt=\"EMB: 524\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=524\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"7\"><img alt=\"EMB: 583\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=583\" border=\"0\" /></td></tr><tr><td class=\"boxleftfill\"></td><td valign=\"middle\" align=\"center\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"middle\" bgcolor=\"#efece4\"><p class=\"textSubHeaders\">General Disclaimer</p><p><span class=\"textQuotes\">The Llama Export referral programme is run at the total discretion and good will of the operators of the Llama Export website the ?Bjorck Brothers? located in Gran Canaria Island, Spain. At any time and without prior notice Llama Export reserves the right to bring the programme to an end or amend the referral programme in any way it sees fit, including but not limited to, the method of points allocation, the number of points awarded for all sales, the total points required in order to receive a gift, as well as the nature and value of gifts provided. </span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></td><td class=\"boxrightfill\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"boxleftfill\" valign=\"bottom\" align=\"left\"><img alt=\"EMB: 582\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=582\" border=\"0\" /></td><td class=\"boxbott\" height=\"7\"><img alt=\"EMB: 524\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=524\" border=\"0\" /></td><td valign=\"bottom\" align=\"right\"><img alt=\"EMB: 581\" src=\"index.php?FuseAction=Asset.Display&as_id=581\" border=\"0\" /></td></tr></tbody></table>\";}','Page',1,'a:8:{s:14:\"LYT_TITLEIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"LYT_MENU_NORMALIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"LYT_MENU_MOUSEOVERIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"LYT_LAYOUT\";s:7:\"default\";s:28:\"LYT_LAYOUT_APPLY_TO_CHILDREN\";s:1:\"1\";s:25:\"LYT_LAYOUT_SUBPAGECONTENT\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"LYT_STYLESHEET\";s:4:\"main\";s:15:\"LYT_WINDOWTITLE\";s:0:\"\";}',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,681,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Intro