nlikely that we will be able to\r\nprevent shipping in time. Therefore you cannot cancel an order once it has been paid.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nContacting Us:If\r\n	you have questions or need to be supplied return address and RMA \r\n	please use our issues system by clicking on this link. We will\r\n	answer any questions usually within 10 hours Members\r\n	page link\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nShipping Address:The shipping address must be a permanent address, we do not ship to temporary holiday accomodation/destinations.Sealed Boxes\r\nThere are times when quality control will complete a final inspection \r\nand break open a box and then reseal, on occasion they forget to reseal.\r\n It is also possible for seals to moisten and drop off while stored in \r\nthe paddock. We can never guarantee you will receive an unopened box.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',0),(2231,'Contact Us',NULL,'2014-02-25 01:33:24',1,'a:1:{s:20:\"AST_PAGE_PAGECONTENT\";s:1182:\"\r\nContact us:<div><br /></div><div>Please log in to the Members area where your questions, issues, etc. will get a ticket and be answered within 10 hours. Most times within the hour.</div><div><br /></div><div>The place to ask about anything including your orders is here:</div><div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><br /></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><span class=\"textSubHeaders\"><a href=\"http://www.llamaexport.com/Members\">http://www.llamaexport.com/Members</a></span><a href=\"http://www.llamaexport.com/Members\"></a></div></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><br /></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\">In the case you cannot get through let us know below so we can get instructions to you:</div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><br /></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font