harge.<br />Please call your bank and authorise an overseas transaction, charging account &quot;AcmeRockets&quot; to charge,<br />then pick up the abandoned \r\norder and follow through.<br /><br />Please note that our support team will not be able to manually place orders for you and cannot force failed transactions.<br /> <br /> For your information:<br /> We have \r\nnoticed a huge increase in the need to authorise transactions with your \r\nbank.<br />You can avoid this by using bitcoin for purchasing. Please go to \r\nFAQs to read more.<br /> <br />\r\n\r\n\";}','Page',0,'a:9:{s:14:\"LYT_TITLEIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"LYT_MENU_NORMALIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"LYT_MENU_MOUSEOVERIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"LYT_LAYOUT\";s:7:\"default\";s:28:\"LYT_LAYOUT_APPLY_TO_CHILDREN\";s:1:\"1\";s:25:\"LYT_LAYOUT_SUBPAGECONTENT\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"LYT_LAYOUT_SECURITYPAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"LYT_STYLESHEET\";s:4:\"main\";s:15:\"LYT_WINDOWTITLE\";s:0:\"\";}',NULL,NULL,NULL,5,2332,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,'\r\nThe charging of your card has failed.Is your card 3D secure enabled? Click here to learn more. You WILL need to enable this.If you have enabled and entered your 3D details and it still fails, your bank could be blocking the charge.Please call your bank and authorise an overseas transaction, charging account &quot;AcmeRockets&quot; to charge,then pick up the abandoned \r\norder and follow through.Please note that our support team will not be able to manually place orders for you and cannot force failed transactions.  For your information: We have \r\nnoticed a huge increase in the need to authorise transactions with your \r\nbank.You can avoid this by using bitcoin for purchasing. Please go to \r\nFAQs to read more. \r\n\r\n',0),(2349,'3D Secure',NULL,'2020-07-08 07:36:40',1,'a:1:{s:20:\"AST_PAGE_PAGECONTENT\";s:2494:\"\r\n<h1>What is 3D Secure?</h1>\r\n    \r\n        \r\n        \r\n \r\n \r\n  <p> 3D Secure adds an authentication step for online payments. We use \r\n3D secure as a fraud prevention measure, as it provides an additional \r\nsecurity layer for online purchases made with credit and debit cards.  </p> \r\n  <p> The intention behind this system is to decrease the risk or credit \r\ncard fraud. We require this extra verification through 3D \r\nsecure, before we process your payment with your bank. <b style=\"background-color: initial;\">If your 3D Secure verification fails, you will not be charged.</b></p><p><br /></p><p> If the 3D Secure verification isn\'t working (possibly due to a \r\nconnection failure or incorrect password) please try the following \r\nsteps: </p> \r\n  <dl><dt>\r\n    Attempt the payment again. Make sure you are entering the correct password or SMS net code. If your bank \r\n    <strong>does not support</strong> 3D Secure or you have not yet enrolled, please refer to the information below.\r\n   </dt><dt><br />\r\n    </dt><dt>Disable your pop-up blocker for a few minutes. 3D Secure opens up \r\nin a additional window that is easily blocked by pop-up blockers.\r\n   </dt></dl> \r\n  <section class=\"callout-yellow\"> \r\n   <h4 id=\"bank\">MasterCard SecureCode/NetCode</h4> \r\n   <p> For 3D Secure transactions as a MasterCard user, you will either \r\nhave created a SecureCode password or your bank will send you a NetCode \r\nvia SMS. You just have to enter either of these when prompted by the 3D \r\nSecure screen. </p> \r\n   <p> If you have not yet enrolled for a MasterCard SecureCode/NetCode you can <a href=\"http://www.mastercard.us/securecode-sign-up.html\" target=\"_blank\"> do it now</a> (if it is supported by your financial institution). </p> \r\n  </section>\r\n  <section class=\"callout-blue\"> \r\n   <h4>Verified by Visa</h4> \r\n   <p> Visa cardholders will either have to enter their pre-determined \r\nsecurity password which they have set up with their financial \r\ninstitution. If you have forgotten this password, you will have to click\r\n the reset password link. The exact process will depend on your bank. </p> \r\n   <p> If you have not yet enrolled with Verified by Visa, you can click <a href=\"http://www.visaeurope.com/en/cardholders/verified_by_visa/sign_up.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">here if you\'re a European Visa cardholder</a> or <a href=\"https://verified.visa.com/aam/activation/landingPage.aam\" target=\"_blank\">here if you\'re an international Visa cardholder</a>. </p> \r\n  </section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\";}','Page',0,'a:9:{s:14:\"LYT_TITLEIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"LYT_MENU_NORMALIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"LYT_MENU_MOUSEOVERIMAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"LYT_LAYOUT\";s:7:\"default\";s:28:\"LYT_LAYOUT_APPLY_TO_CHILDREN\";s:1:\"1\";s:25:\"LYT_LAYOUT_SUBPAGECONTENT\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"LYT_LAYOUT_SECURITYPAGE\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"LYT_STYLESHEET\";s:4:\"main\";s:15:\"LYT_WINDOWTITLE\";s:0:\"\";}',NULL,NULL,NULL,6,2332,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,'\r\nWhat is 3D Secure?\r\n    \r\n        \r\n        \r\n \r\n \r\n   3D Secure adds an authentication step for online payments. We use \r\n3D secure as a fraud prevention measure, as it provides an additional \r\nsecurity layer for online purchases made with credit and debit cards.   \r\n   The intention behind this system is to decrease the risk or credit \r\ncard fraud. We require this extra verification through 3D \r\nsecure, before we process your payment with your bank. If your 3D Secure verification fails, you will not be charged. If the 3D Secure verification isn\'t working (possibly due to a \r\nconnection failure or incorrect password) please try the following \r\nsteps:  \r\n  \r\n    Attempt the payment again. Make sure you are entering the correct password or SMS net code. If your bank \r\n    does not support 3D Secure or you have not yet enrolled, please refer to the information below.\r\n   \r\n    Disable your pop-up blocker for a few minutes. 3D Secure opens up \r\nin a additional window that is easily blocked by pop-up blockers.\r\n    \r\n   \r\n   MasterCard SecureCode/NetCode \r\n    For 3D Secure transactions as a MasterCard user, you will either \r\nhave created a SecureCode password or your bank will send you a NetCode \r\nvia SMS. You just have to enter either of these when prompted by the 3D \r\nSecure screen.  \r\n    If you have not yet enrolled for a MasterCard SecureCode/NetCode you can  do it now (if it is supported by your financial institution).  \r\n  \r\n   \r\n   Verified by Visa \r\n    Visa cardholders will either have to enter their pre-determined \r\nsecurity password which they have set up with their financial \r\ninstitution. If you have forgotten this password, you will have to click\r\n the reset password link. The exact process will depend on your bank.  \r\n    If you have not yet enrolled with Verified by Visa, you can click here if you\'re a European Visa cardholder or here if you\'re an international Visa cardholder.  \r\n  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',0);
